{"tid":839772,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施治係FIFA入面......","createTime":"2018-09-28T07:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T15:12:18.000Z","uid":10176,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"34fdb50715e16bc5adbe03c5cb1124be4bc7211e","tid":839772,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴門將施治平時戴頭套比賽，已成一個象徵，但不代表他吃飯睡覺也要戴上頭套，但由EA Sports推出的電玩遊戲新一輯《FIFA 19》，似乎不明這個道理，被發現施治在與球會傾談新合約時，一樣戴上比賽時用的頭套。<br />\n《FIFA 19》周五正式推出，有球迷發現遊戲中有趣一幕，就是當玩職業模式（Career Mode）時，施治穿上西裝與球會傾合約或轉會，仍會戴上頭套進入辦公室。遊戲中的施治無法除下頭套，不管是程式上限制抑或設計者太懶，但這樣抽離現實，連施治本人都在Twitter上留言自嘲：「錯了各位......我會戴領帶」<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，有網民還笑指施治在《FIFA 19》的樣貌，與英國查理斯王子很相似。</span><br />\n施治之所以一直戴住頭套比賽，全因效力車路士時有段不愉快經歷，在2006/07球季對陣雷丁的比賽，被對方中場史堤夫亨特用膝蓋撞頭而一度昏迷，賽後證實頭骨出現裂痕，要休戰3個月才能再次重返球場，令他及後因有心理陰影，直至現在都一直要戴上頭套比賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180928/large/1538106757_6c1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180928%2Flarge%2F1538106757_6c1f.jpg&h=15fbca97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180928/58732908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58732908&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa080%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9e1e5df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58732908&h=89e07824\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180928/58732908</a>"},{"pid":"bb9a7a81ca2acc3a35df8425e0cc78c7d1a32809","tid":839772,"uid":23655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a74ab40bec5947eb739109a2225be916e899