0c91631216c12bba494","tid":839772,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"同球會傾合約咁危險緊係要帶頭盔啦"},{"pid":"4fb19c934025e59a5d5f31fc65dbd463693d3ac3","tid":839772,"uid":20738,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181004&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=58756622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181004%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D58756622&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa080%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5e3a1177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181004%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D58756622&h=2c1ae3e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181004&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=58756622</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/224714_f7a524a7579c3cb4f1ed626b4045879c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F224714_f7a524a7579c3cb4f1ed626b4045879c.png&h=02635815&s={SIZE}\" />除頭套打番呔 施治FIFA 19華麗轉身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/224742_c102036a0dd6ea1311a9b50024140f56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F224742_c102036a0dd6ea1311a9b50024140f56.png&h=3b48c3d4&s={SIZE}\" />施治終於唔使戴頭套入office<br />\n<br />\n施治之前Twitter話最好打番條呔，EA Sports亦聽佢話換條紅呔畀佢。<br />\n新推出的足球電子遊戲《FIFA 19》，之前被網民恥笑阿仙奴門將施治，在遊戲的「職業模式（Career Mode）」中戴住龍門頭套去辦公室傾合約，結果生產商EA Sports聽從民意，先在PC版作出修訂：施治終於除下頭套，還戴上一條紅色領呔出現在辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n相信EA Sports之前偷懶，在既定程式中沒有為球場內外的施治設定不同造型，結果施治連走入辦公室也戴住頭套，貽笑大方，連施治本人也在Twitter留言，自嘲說應該戴呔才對，結果EA Sports果然在報道推出後照單全收，進行改良，而PC版則是第一步的修訂，看看除下頭套、戴上一條紅色呔的施治，是否獲網民或球迷受落。<br />\n<br />\n除了施治外，《FIFA 19》亦有其他修訂已作，包括播放歐聯會歌的時間已校正，以及射門動作的一些小改動。"},{"pid":"12c5504df498f7cb1b562253f35a965016f13ba0","tid":839772,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fb19c934025e59a5d5f31fc65dbd463693d3ac3","tid":839772,"uid":20738,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181004&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=58756622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181004%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D58756622&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa080%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5e3a1177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181004%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D58756622&h=2c1ae3e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181004&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=58756622</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/224714_f7a524a7579c3cb4f1ed626b4045879c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F224714_f7a524a7579c3cb4f1ed626b4045879c.png&h=02635815&s={SIZE}\" />除頭套打番呔 施治FIFA 19華麗轉身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/224742_c102036a0dd6ea1311a9b50024140f56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F224742_c102036a0dd6ea1311a9b50024140f56.png&h=3b48c3d4&s={SIZE}\" />施治終於唔使戴頭套入office<br />\n<br />\n施治之前Twitter話最好打番條呔，EA Sports亦聽佢話換條紅呔畀佢。<br />\n新推出的足球電子遊戲《FIFA 19》，之前被網民恥笑阿仙奴門將施治，在遊戲的「職業模式（Career Mode）」中戴住龍門頭套去辦公室傾合約，結果生產商EA Sports聽從民意，先在PC版作出修訂：施治終於除下頭套，還戴上一條紅色領呔出現在辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n相信EA Sports之前偷懶，在既定程式中沒有為球場內外的施治設定不同造型，結果施治連走入辦公室也戴住頭套，貽笑大方，連施治本人也在Twitter留言，自嘲說應該戴呔才對，結果EA Sports果然在報道推出後照單全收，進行改良，而PC版則是第一步的修訂，看看除下頭套、戴上一條紅色呔的施治，是否獲網民或球迷受落。<br />\n<br />\n除了施治外，《FIFA 19》亦有其他修訂已作，包括播放歐聯會歌的時間已校正，以及射門動作的一些小改動。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"變左M額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/goo